✨ Features


Add tasks — quickly create new to-dos with a title (and optional due date / priority).
Mark as done — check off completed tasks and track your progress.
Edit & delete — update a task's text or remove it entirely.
Filter view — switch between All, Active, and Completed.
Persistent storage — tasks are saved in the browser (localStorage), so they survive page reloads.
Responsive design — works on desktop, tablet, and mobile.
Clear completed — remove all finished tasks in one click.



